{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Raise the 40% tax threshold from \u00a350,271 to \u00a353,800",
        "additional_details": "I think that raising the threshold to \u00a353,800 would help account for inflation and wage growth, ensuring that higher tax rates apply to genuinely high earners.",
        "background": "I believe the current 40% tax threshold of \u00a350,271 is outdated and doesn't reflect current earnings or inflation. I think that many middle-income earners\u2014such as teachers, nurses, and skilled professionals\u2014are now being pushed into the higher tax bracket. ",
